These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cabbage, carrot, garlic
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, german, brazilian, canadian
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, mauve, blue, ebony
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, dubstep, electronic
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, swisher, prince, chaman
 1. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 2. the german is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 3. the canadian is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 4. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 5. the fan of classical is the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the fan of d&b is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 7. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person eating carrot is on the left of the colombian##1
 9. the person who likes blue is the person eating asparagus##1
10. the prince-smoker is the person who likes mauve##1
11. the colombian is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | cabbage    | carrot      | asparagus  | garlic     |
| Nationality         | canadian    | brazilian   | colombian | german      |
| Color   | mauve       | azure | blue     | ebony    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | d&b         | classical  | dubstep    |
| Cigar           | prince      | chaman       | blend | swisher |

