.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, hot-chocolate
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, russian, polish, colombian
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, scooter, subway, ship
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, pony, rat
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, fishing, gardening, puzzles
 1. the russian is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person driving the ship is on the right of the italian##1
 8. the owner of the hamster is the person driving the ship##1
 9. the polish is the person driving the subway##1
10. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | coffee      | 7up     | fanta    | hot-chocolate |
| Nationality   | italian | russian   | polish   | colombian           |
| Transport   | scooter  | ship     | subway    | skateboard         |
| Pet           | rat         | hamster | pony     | ferret        |
| Hobby         | photography     | puzzles  | fishing | gardening       |

