.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, cauliflower, grapes, lettuce
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, grey, purple, white
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, july, february, may
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, snowboarding, tennis, weightlifting
4 different games are played: billiard, go, backgammon, bridge
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 3. the person eating grapes is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 4. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the person playing bridge is the person eating grapes##1
 7. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 8. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 9. the person who likes white is the person who's birthday is in july##1
10. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
11. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
12. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Food          | cabbage    | lettuce      | grapes  | cauliflower   |
| Color   | white     | purple      | grey | blue      |
| Birthday           | july       | december         | may  | february         |
| Sport         | basketball | snowboarding | tennis  | weightlifting |
| Game     | backgammon       | billiard         | bridge   | go        |

