.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, soy-milk, sprite
There 4 different types of food: garlic, grapefruit, pepper, raspberry
City: miami, nizza, paris, rome
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, june, july, december
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, aquamarine, turquise, ivory
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
 5. the person who likes lilac is on the far left##1
 6. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 9. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
12. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | sprite   | cola      | coffee     |
| Food          | pepper     | garlic   | raspberry | grapefruit |
| City   | nizza | paris | miami   | rome       |
| Birthday           | june       | april      | december     | july |
| Color     | lilac    | turquise     | ivory     | aquamarine     |

