 4. the person who growsazalea is the person eating potato##1
 5. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person eating mango##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
 7. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 8. the person who growsdaffodil is the person drinking milk##1
 9. the person eating pumpkin is the person who growsmarigold##1
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
11. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
12. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
13. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
14. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
