The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, october, january, july
4 different pets are kept: snake, horse, fish, frog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, rugby, snowboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, van
 1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 3. the person traveling to prague is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 6. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
 7. the person driving the ship is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
10. the person who's sport is rugby is the person driving the van##1
11. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who's birthday is in september##1
12. the owner of the fish is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| City         | venice   | liverpool | prague    | berlin  |
| Birthday   | july    | september | january      | october |
| Pet   | fish | snake | frog         | horse  |
| Sport         | climbing  | rugby     | snowboarding | cricket     |
| Transport     | bike      | van       | ship         | car         |

