 6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 8. the person watching family movies is on the right of the tower house##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
10. the person watching family movies is on the left of the colonial house##1
11. the person watching family movies is the person who's birthday is in april##1
12. the palace house is on the far right##1

