 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing scrabble is the person who growsdaisy##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person driving the trike##1
 7. the fan of salsa is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 8. the person drinking cola is the person playing chess##1
 9. the fan of disco is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
10. the person who growszinnia is the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing chess##1
12. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
13. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |      3       |       4       |
