 5. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 6. the mexican is on the far left##1
 7. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person driving the subway##1
10. the person traveling to boston is the owner of the dog##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the canadian##1
12. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| City    | san-francisco     | colone  | boston       | paris      |
| Nationality       | mexican    | egyptian        | nigerian  | canadian      |
| Cigar         | old-henry  | aristoff | pall-mall | alhambra |
| Pet         | chinchilla | mouse          | dog         | hamster      |
| Transport   | subway     | helicopter     | trike       | van          |

