.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, airplane, trike, train
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, magic-tricks, video-games, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller, western
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, june, december, july
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, golf, surfing, ice-hockey
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
 2. the person driving the airplane is the person watching western movies##1
 3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person driving the trike##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person driving the train##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 9. the person who's sport is golf is the person watching thriller movies##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
